[The state of Texas can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/77N1. Abilene can be seen on the map at http://www.bestplaces.net/images/city/abilene_tx.gif.

Rabies is almost always fatal; there are very few humans that have survived and sadly, there are likely no animals that have survived. Any mammal is susceptible to rabies, therefore it is extremely important to vaccinate your pets, even horses or cattle, to protect them and to build a barrier between the disease and yourself. - Mod.TG]
